plot: A June 1967 NBC News critical examination of New Orleans District Attorney Jim Garrison's investigation into a conspiracy to assassinate President Kennedy allegedly masterminded by prominent New Orleans businessman Clay Shaw.
title: The JFK Conspiracy: The Case of Jim Garrison
